"OPEN OR CLOSE THE TREE FILE
nnoremap <silent> <C-b> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>

"FAST WAY FOR SAVE
nnoremap <C-s> :w<Cr>

"FAST WAY FROM QUIT"
nnoremap <C-Q> :wq!<CR>

"SWITCH BETWEEN OPEN FILE
nnoremap <C-SPACE> <C-w>w
"nnoremap <C-SHIFT-SPACE> <C-w>

"Use Alt (M) form the resize window
nnoremap <M-l> :vertical resize -2<CR>
nnoremap <M-h> :vertical resize +2<CR>
nnoremap <M-j> :resize -2<CR>
nnoremap <M-k> :resize +2<CR>
